{"tid":1359214,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"袁志偉笑握屠夫手 全城震怒","createTime":"2019-07-24T05:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:55:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c3cd1bb6a71c0ac19cdf1e1dd4007708c987c9","tid":1359214,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190724/20736342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F20736342&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=11c8efec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F20736342&h=3f4bc7ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190724/20736342</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n袁志偉笑握屠夫手 全城震怒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190724/large/1563901147_e39e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190724%2Flarge%2F1563901147_e39e.jpg&h=cec4ca69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁志偉獨家訪問李鵬，其間笑容滿面與李親切握手，被巿民唾棄。《壹週刊》圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】六四事件後的1990年7月，無綫新聞部派出記者袁志偉獨家訪問李鵬，袁笑容滿面地與李親切握手，成為本港新聞史上一個經典場面。袁志偉的做法遭巿民唾棄，更稱無綫為「走狗台」。經此一役，無綫新聞報道明顯靠攏當權者，日積月累下，成為網民眼中的「CCTVB」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190724/large/1563901145_fca9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190724%2Flarge%2F1563901145_fca9.jpg&h=456d9a8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1989年的《民主歌聲獻中華》中，跑馬地現場曾舉起抗議李鵬的標語。支聯會圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年無綫收視暴跌<br />\n<br />\n袁志偉的李鵬專訪累及無綫在該段時間的收視暴跌17點，同時期的亞洲電視的收視率則微升3點，收視佔有率達51%，罕有超越無綫。已退休的浸會大學新聞系前助理教授杜耀明指出，李鵬當年支持武力鎮壓學生，導致血灑天安門六四屠城事件，採訪價值當然極其重要，但作為專業記者應專業地質詢其屠城責任，而非跟這位千夫所指人物握手，「我睇唔到訪問有質詢李鵬，相反，同行另一名無綫記者李汶靜迴避與李鵬握手，做法專業」。<br />\n<br />\n杜耀明續稱，「握手」事件前，無綫新聞對六四報道一直十分專業；但袁志偉握手一役後，無綫新聞報道明顯對權力靠攏，日積月累下，無綫淪為不少港人眼中的「CCTVB」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者蔡朗清  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n林振強黃霑二創寸「慈祥鵬」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n訃告重用「反革命暴亂」形容民運"},{"pid":"47e037c14be253f898c48abad3f70c91b9def39b","tid":1359214,"uid":118056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:16:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6595ab75fde6313e3027f605ded6b4811fc9bd3","tid":1359214,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"笑握死神手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd8dcd057aa3b56804e19bb36835df44d638dc5","tid":1359214,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"條人渣響tvb做足咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a120f067e81e33de0c28a4d3956df005e109e29","tid":1359214,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"六叔又係嘅，有眼無珠，自己在生果時都唔炒左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9fc95f44870a29b4aa9b0bc3fcb72bd32ae151","tid":1359214,"uid":274289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"袁志偉發跡史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實証明 中共政權底下<br />\n<br />\n你肯屏棄禮義廉恥 就有得升官發財"},{"pid":"329b9abc58f62ad9270082c09d2b0f68694dd24e","tid":1359214,"uid":104502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"30年香港人爭取到啲乜？<br />\n當年唔阻止主權移交真係好撚on9"}]}